author: kristian
title: kristian
text:
Great first purchase. Super happy with the product! Was very sceptical as to how long the shipping would take as i live in norway and i was expecting customs to hold it for atleast a week or two. Product came after 5 days of orderings. I do bjj and mma and havnt been sore once since i started my CBD journey. Our gym loves it!
Edit: The product i ordered was the RAW Hemp Oil Drops 300mg CBD+CBDa (3%).
